description: Fixed the issue with the mod breaking, Biomes Included: Oasis, Mountain, Rainforest, Ice. Oasis a desert type biome with trees by the water and dead trees on the inner land, Mountain a mountain type biome with a rock only texture and some sand for beaches, Ranforest a biome covered in trees with sand for beaches, Icey a complete ice type biome with no other textures, only ice
